title: iCTF 2024 -- High School Track
content:
iCTF 2024 -- High School Track

Welcome to the 2024 iCTF, High School Track!

For information about the competition check out https://ictf.cs.ucsb.edu.

For help and support, check the #ictf-2024 Discord channel https://ictf.cs.ucsb.edu/discord.


The 2024 iCTF is organized by the ACTION NSF AI Institute in collaboration with Shellphish, and with support from the Women in Computer Science at UCSB.


Cash prizes provided by Activision!
